WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:08.440
Antonio Cassano was met with jubilant crowds as he returned to the Sampdoria training ground today.

00:00:08.560 --> 00:00:17.700
Hordes of fans descended on the Centro Sportivo Mugnaini in Bogliasco for the Blucerchiati’s second session of the day.

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:30.800
And while the squad was training this morning, Antonio Cassano was putting his signature on a two-year deal that’ll keep him at the club until 30 June 2017.

00:00:31.020 --> 00:00:38.680
Present during the signing were Samp sporting director Carlo Osti and the player’s lawyer.

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:48.840
Lunch followed at the Hotel Nastor in Nervi, with Sampdoria coach Walter Zenga also joining.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:55.180
It was a chance for Zenga and Cassano to lay the foundations for the Bari-born star’s second stint with the Blucerchiati.

00:00:55.257 --> 00:01:00.997
Later this afternoon, Cassano joined his team-mates for training, wasting no time in serving up an array of assists for his offensive colleagues.

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:07.180
There where whoops and cheers from the watching fans, as Cassano entertained them with his trademark plays.

